{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "恶魔诱惑下的虚假乐园第5话 使徒VS使徒",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "法斯静候弗拉斯并对其设下陷阱。\\n然而，里莎相信弗拉斯是清白的，\\n而挡在了法斯身前。弗拉斯则趁机\\n净化了附在皮诺身上的瘴气，\\n道出她被植入了虚假记忆一事。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "乐园 集会地前",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "乐母现在正进行集会。\\n只要在这里等着，觊觎封印石的\\n弗拉斯前辈应该就会现身。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "我们真的要与弗拉斯交战吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "如果真为了弗拉斯前辈好，\\n我们就应该阻止他。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "是……这样吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加百列",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "加百列，你怎么了？\\n好像连你也情绪低落了啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加百列",
            "context": "小皮背着我接受了命令\\n这件事……\\n也许是令人开心的成长吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加百列",
            "context": "可是，为什么呢？\\n我莫名地觉得现在的她\\n不太对劲……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120217_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "他来了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "法斯……你果然来村子里了。\\n我就猜到只要我一靠近\\n封印石，你就会现身……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "但没想到你已经\\n和皮诺他们会合了……\\n被你抢先了一步啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "你复活恶魔的企图已经因为\\n奎茵的秘密调查昭然若揭！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "奎茵的秘密调查……\\n原来如此，\\n事情变成了这样啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120217_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "关于对你的处置，奎茵已经全权\\n委托给我。我会根据你的危险程度\\n对你实行抓捕或就地正法。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120217_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "你因一己私欲杀害无辜村民，\\n我不会对你手下留情。\\n以神威之名，执行任务。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "唔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "法斯，我来掩护你！\\n加百列，赐予我力量吧！\\n圣痕，解放！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_01",
                "110366_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "里莎前辈和尤蒂尔\\n去包围弗拉斯前辈，\\n别让他跑了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "好，知道了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "我要上了！哈啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "要同时对付两个使徒\\n还是有些吃力。但是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "招数毫无章法，\\n不像你平时冷静的作风。\\n你很焦急吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120217_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "你果然很危险……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "（我……继续袖手旁观\\n真的好吗……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "（的确如皮诺所说，\\n间接证据也许是齐了。但是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "虽然你不擅长逻辑思考，\\n但你的直觉很准。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "这是我所欠缺的才能。\\n稍微拿出点自信来。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "（我害怕插手那场战斗。\\n但是，我……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120217_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "你露出破绽了，束手就擒吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "呃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "等、等一下！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "里莎！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120217_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "里莎，你这是做什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "我、我还是觉得很奇怪！\\n不能就这样断定弗拉斯是坏人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120217_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "间接证据已经齐了。\\n你有足以推翻证据的依据吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "没有！但是……\\n我的直觉告诉我，他不是坏人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "里莎前辈，请你让开。\\n他的罪行是通过奎茵的\\n秘密调查……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "皮诺你也放下弓箭！\\n奎茵的命令真的对吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "你在说什么傻话！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "里莎……你的直觉果然敏锐，\\n虽然以这种形式公布真相\\n非我本意……哈啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "呀啊啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加百列",
            "context": "小皮！\\n弗拉斯，你扔了什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "装了圣水的皮袋。\\n这是我在跟你们分开的时候\\n用手头的圣水准备的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "以汝之名赐我荣光。\\n我将化为万民之救赎，\\n赐予祝圣之人无上的安息。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "唔……啊啊……\\n啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这是！？有瘴气\\n从皮诺的身体里出来了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "这是封印石的瘴气。\\n她被瘴气移植了记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "也就是奎茵进行秘密调查\\n并对皮诺下达了命令的\\n虚假记忆。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加百列",
            "context": "这……怎么会！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "难道是乐母搞的鬼吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加百列",
            "context": "可是，自从进入村子之后，\\n我一直都和小皮在一起。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210145_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "加百列",
            "context": "要是乐母动过手脚，\\n我一定会发现的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "她的记忆是来潜伏之前被篡改的。\\n不是有人说在我们潜伏进来之前，\\n乐母曾与一个男人幽会吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯，我记得\\n说是乐母送了礼物……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "那并不是送礼物……\\n而是借出了封印石。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "那个男人接触了潜伏行动前的皮诺，\\n给她移植了虚假的记忆，\\n然后将封印石还给了乐母。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你说什么！？如果是这样，\\n那个男人究竟是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "目击了幽会现场的女子\\n清楚地记得那个人的长相。\\n她向我讲述了那个人的具体特征。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "她之所以被杀是为了封口，\\n防止有除了我以外的人\\n知道他的真实身份。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110382_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "弗拉斯",
            "context": "对吧……法斯？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120217_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110381_03"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "里莎",
            "context": "法斯他……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "等一下！\\n法斯怎么会做那种事！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "法斯可是使徒的榜样！\\n对绑架事件进行搜查的时候\\n他也……唔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "我很看好你。\\n不要让我失望哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "皮诺",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "话说你的下一个任务\\n是前往乐园进行秘密搜查吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110366_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "法斯",
            "context": "既然如此，我就送你这个\\n为你饯行，收下吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20833_05_0068",
